  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "If a deployment transaction has a gas limit that exceeds the block gas limit, Hardhat will throw an error with a `trying to deploy a contract whose code is too large` message, which is wrong.\r\n\r\nInstead, it should return a `Transaction gas limit is M and exceeds block gas limit of N` error.\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/3404#issuecomment-1346849400 for more context.",
